      "title": "IMF announces $2.9 billion loan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is announced that Sri Lanka will receive an extended funding facility of $2.9 billion from the International Monetary Fund in the future.",
        "The International Monetary Fund stated in the press conference that Sri Lanka and the International Monetary Fund have reached a staff level agreement.",
        "There, its representatives mentioned that this facility will be operational for 48 months."
